'''Costruzioni Italiane Serrature e Affini''', also known by the acronym '''CISA''', is an Italian manufacturer of [[Lock (security device)|lock]]ing and [[access control|access control systems]].
==History== Costruzioni Italiane Serrature e Affini was founded in [[Florence, Italy|Florence]], by Luigi Bucci in 1926. The company is part of [[Allegion]].<ref>{{cite web|title=CISA web site|url=http://www.cisa.com/EN/company/Pages/History.aspx|accessdate=27 March 2011}}</ref>
